#: ../../modules/backends/backends_qilisim.rst:134
msgid ""
"Adaptive step size; ``tol`` bounds the fidelity error between the RK4 and"
" RK5 estimates."
msgstr ""
"Mida de pas adaptativa; ``tol`` limita l'error de fidelitat entre les "
"estimacions RK4 i RK5."

