msgstr "Krylov / Arnoldi"

#: ../../modules/backends/backends_qilisim.rst:137
msgid ""
"Can offer decent scaling for large sparse Hamiltonians; tune ``dim`` for "
"the Krylov subspace size."
msgstr ""
"Pot oferir un escalat decent per a Hamiltonians dispersos grans; ajusteu "
"``dim`` per a la mida del subespai de Krylov."

